# ==============================================================================
# OMISSION LIST EXAMPLE / RESUME LOG
# ==============================================================================
#
# CASE 1: Scenes rendered at 100% (Completely skipped)
06_01
06_02

# CASE 2: Background pass crash. Resumes background render (f) from frame 150 to 300.
# (The character pass is ignored because it was already completed)
06_03 f 150 300

# CASE 3: Character pass crash. Resumes character render (p) from frame 50 to 120.
# (We use dashes '-' as placeholders so the 'p' falls exactly in column 5)
06_04 - - - p 50 120

# CASE 4: Missing frames for both the background and character passes.
06_05 f 100 200 p 100 200
